<br>
I too did a test, about medding while running on a horse. Here was my test.<br>
<br>
Burn mana until I was down to about 50m. Stand in place to regen. I no longer have my notes, but it was something like 2 minutes. time &quot;x&quot;. This is my regen time with KEI + Meditating (since we have assumed standing on a horse while motionless is medding)<br>
